    "html_format": "<div class=\"document-view-wrapper\">\n<style>\n.html-preview * {font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: 12pt;}\n.html-preview a.NoteRef {text-decoration: none;}\n.html-preview table td {vertical-align: top;}\n.html-preview table {width: 100%;}\n.html-preview p {white-space: pre-wrap;}\n.html-preview .leading {width: 4px; display: inline-block;}\n.html-preview hr {height: 1px; padding: 0; margin: 1em 0; border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #CCC;}\n.html-preview .Normal {className: Normal; margin-bottom: 8pt;}\n.html-preview .a3 {font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;}\n.html-preview .a4 td {border: 1px solid #000;}\n.html-preview .a5 {className: a5; text-indent: 48px;}\n</style>\n<div class=\"html-preview\">\n<style>.html-preview{width: 761px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-top: 93px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-bottom: 32px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-left: 34px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-right: 105px}</style><p style=\"text-align: center; text-indent: 330.8px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-2\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold;\">{#2}Ходим ишлайдиган ташкилот номи</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold;\"> раҳбари </span><span class=\"structures structure-3\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold;\">{#3}Ташкилот раҳбарининг Ф.И.Оси</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold;\">га</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; text-indent: 330.8px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-4\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold;\">{#4}Ходим ишлайдиган бўлим ва ходимнинг лавозими</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold;\">си </span><span class=\"structures structure-5\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold;\">{#5}Ходимнинг Ф.И.Оси</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold;\">дан</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold;\">АРИЗА</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 56.666666666667px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">Меҳнат кодекси 407-моддаси “Икки ёшга тўлмаган боланинг ота-онасидан бирига (васийсига) дам олиш ва овқатланиш учун танаффусдан ташқари болани овқатлантириш учун қўшимча танаффуслар берилади. Бу танаффуслар камида ҳар уч соатда, ҳар бири ўттиз минутдан кам бўлмаган давомийликда берилади. Икки ёшга тўлмаган икки ёки ундан ортиқ фарзанди бўлган тақдирда, танаффуснинг давомийлиги камида бир соат қилиб белгиланади. Болани овқатлантириш учун танаффуслар иш вақтига киритилади ва ўртача иш ҳақи бўйича ҳақ тўланади” ҳамда ушбу аризамга асосан менга 2 ёшга тўлмаган фарзандимни кунлик овқатлантириш учун қўшимча танафффус беришингизни ва ушбу танаффус вақтини ҳар куни соат </span><span class=\"structures structure-7\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">{#7}Танаффус бериш бошланадиган соат</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">дан </span><span class=\"structures structure-8\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">{#8}Танаффус тугайдиган соат</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">гача ҳамда соат </span><span class=\"structures structure-7\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">{#7}Танаффус бериш бошланадиган соат</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">дан соат </span><span class=\"structures structure-8\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">{#8}Танаффус тугайдиган соат</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">гача қилиб белгилашингизни сўрайман.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 56.666666666667px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">Боламнинг туғилганлик ҳақидаги гувоҳномаси нусхасини илова қиляпман.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 56.666666666667px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-5\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">{#5}Ходимнинг Ф.И.Оси</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span class=\"structures structure-9\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">{#9}Ариза ёзилган сана</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 56.666666666667px;\"></p>\n</div></div>",
